              <h3>The Backstory</h3>
              <p>Yo! We’re Bort and Caleb, founders of Nightshade. Early on this path, we were both simply concerned about improving our access to fresh herbs… so we started growing our own. Immediately, we noticed the bump in flavor and freshness, not to mention the convenience of walking out our back door rather than running out to the store.</p>
              <p>We produced less waste, created habitat for pollinators, and found fulfillment in watching our plants flourish. We found a creative outlet in selecting plants that complemented our favorite cooking styles and cocktail recipes. We started to get a little crazier and now grow bizarre, beautiful, and delicious herbs, fruit, flowers, and veggies from around the world. It evokes an honest sense of pride and fulfillment to snip off a couple sprigs from you own lemon thyme plant and use that astounding aroma and flavor to bring out the highest potential in your own inspired culinary creation. We’re hardcode home cooks, cocktail enthusiasts, DC natives, and big fans of living the Good Life…join us on this journey!</p>
