              <h3>Bort</h3>
              <p>It started as most great adventures do -- with a stiff drink. I believe it was a “South Side,” a classic libation made with gin and fresh mint. You see, when I set out to refine my cocktail crafting skills, I quickly realized two things. First, drinks made with fresh herbs are amazing. Second, it’s expensive and wasteful to buy those herbs at the store. The solution was obvious, and what started as a few plants on a window sill has grown into a full fledged passion project. I now maintain my own sprawling balcony oasis, which I keep stocked with as many tasty herbs and beautiful vine flowers as possible.</p>
              <p>I love building things and sharing my interests with others. Be it a piece of software or a crazy-cool plant installation, I find immense joy in taking a concept and shaping it into reality. I believe life is short, and it should be spent eating the best food, drinking the best drinks, and generally enjoying the best that this green earth has to offer.</p>
